These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, camping
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Hobby   | camping | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Sport   | baseball | volleyball |

 #################################

 
